title: 12/07: Start or Sit (NFC); Oh, Henry! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
So, did you start Derrick Henry? Of course you didn't! But let's all marvel at how great he was and discuss his rest of season outlook along with Leonard Fournette's before we have some rankings debates (8:30) about the MIN offense, David Johnson and Mitchell Trubisky ... Our final thoughts on the Waiver Wire RBs (17:08), the Startometer (21:18) for the DET-ARI and NYG-WAS games plus Beat the Waiver Wire (22:33) ... MIN-SEA (25:00), LAR-CHI (32:30), NO-TB (39:30), ATL-GB (48:10), DEN-SF (51:51), PHI-DAL (54:50), DET-ARI (58:01), NYG-WAS (1:00:04) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
